 snow avalanching in Iceland (2003) Geophysical Research Letters, (58), pp. 1-4; López-Bustins, J.A., (2007), p. 184. , The Western Mediterranean Oscillation and Rainfall in the Catalan Pyrenees. PhD Thesis. Department of Physical Geography and Regional Geographical Analysis, University of Barcelona. CataloniaLópez-Moreno, J.I., Vicente-Serrano, M., Atmospheric circulation influence on the interannual variability of the snow pack in the Spanish Pyrenees during the second half of the 20th century (2007) Nordic Hidrology, 38 (1), pp. 33-44; Martin-Vide, J., Fernández, D., El índice NAO y la precipitación mensual en la España Peninsular (The NAO index and the monthly precipitation in the Peninsular Iberian) (2001) Investigaciones Geográficas, 26, pp. 41-58; Martín-Vide, J., Lopez-Bustins, J.A., The Western Mediterranean Oscillation and Rainfall in the Iberian Peninsula (2006) International Journal of Climatology, 26 (11), pp. 1455-1475; Martín-Vide, J., Barriendos, M., Peña, J.C., Llasat, M.C., Rodríguez, R., (1999) Potencialidad del índice NAO en la previsión de episodios de alta pluviometría en España. Análisis, GR 67, pp. 19-29; Martín-Vide, J., Sánchez-Lorenzo, A., López-Bustins, J.A., Cordobilla, M.J., García-Manuel, A., Raso, J.M., Torrential rainfall in Northeast of Iberian Peninsula: Synoptic patterns and WeMO influence (2008) Advances in Science and Research, 2, pp. 99-105; Milligan, G.W., An examination of the effect of six types of error perturbation on fifteen clustering algorithms (1980) Psychometrika, 45 (3), pp. 325-342; Muntán, E., García-Sellés, C., Oller, P., Martí, G., García, A., Gutiérrez, E., Reconstructing snow avalanches in the Southeastern Pyrenees (2009) Natural Hazards and Earth Systems Sciences, 9, pp. 1599-1612; Oller, P., Muntán, E., Marturià, J., García, C., García, A., Martínez, P., The Avalanche Data in the Eastern Pyrenees. 20 Years of Avalanche Mapping (2006) Proceedings of the International Snow and Science Workshop, pp. 305-313. , T